that really you want to invest the most resources

00:38:17.130 --> 00:38:21.859
in to provide that value to yourself, to the
other people in your life.

00:38:21.859 --> 00:38:28.799
So 3 to 5 areas that really you want to focus
on this year to reach your potential.

00:38:28.799 --> 00:38:31.490
The tactics then, are the second part.

00:38:31.490 --> 00:38:37.050
The tactics are activities are the things
that you're actually going to do to realize

00:38:37.050 --> 00:38:38.710
those strategies.

00:38:38.710 --> 00:38:41.710
