00:38:49.230 --> 00:38:51.060
on an individual level.

00:38:51.060 --> 00:38:54.580
Empathy, teaching and growth those are our
three strategic themes.

00:38:54.580 --> 00:39:00.950
Those are the areas we want to invest our
time and our talent into.

00:39:00.950 --> 00:39:07.539
